This ability must be used in the challenge round, and will go into effect in the elimination round. Once per game, Hathor may replace the elimination with a Chain of Love. Hathor gains immunity and begins the chain by choosing one player as her love, granting them immunity. Players who have immunity from the challenge do not participate in the Chain of Love.
